snippet.title: Top 10 Things You Missed In A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms Episode 3
snippet.description:
Did you catch all these hidden gems and foreshadowing? Join us as we explore the subtle details and Easter eggs carefully planted throughout the third episode of Dunk and Egg's adventure! From symbolic salt beef to historical references, these clever inclusions enhance the story in ways casual viewers might have missed. Our countdown includes Hard Salt Beef Symbolism, The Tragedy at Summerhall prophecy, Brienne's connection to Ser Duncan, Aerion's madness revealed through the puppet show, House Hardyng's honor, and much more! The episode finally reveals Egg's true Targaryen identity, with numerous clues scattered throughout. Did you spot these details or catch something we didn't? Let us know in the comments below!
